title: Husky Liners Quad Caps Product Video
description: Protect your truck's bed rails from scratches and dents caused by everyday wear and tear with Husky Quad Caps™. Each truck bed rail is protected by a 2-piece cap; once installed the seam is completely hidden by the cap's unique styling. Manufactured from highly durable TPO material... Husky Quad Caps™ are thicker and stronger than most other bed rail cap protectors on the market and come with a lifetime guarantee against cracking and breaking. Rugged styling with a factory matched look. Quad Caps™ include removable stake pocket covers and install easily with 3M™ foam tape.
tags: Husky Liners, Quad Caps, Bed Caps, Truck Bed Caps
